§ Definition ⦉
¶ ⦊
  ‖ Given nonzero $x ∈ 𝗥^n$, the ❬half-line❭ emanating from $x$
    is the set
    ◇ ⦊
      ‖ \Set{λx}{λ ≥ 1} ⦉
    ⦉⦉

  ‖ A ❬ray❭ through $x$ or in the direction of $x$ is the set
    ◇ ⦊
      ‖ \Set{λx}{x ≥ 0} ⦉
    ⦉⦉
⦉

